Hey I I checked with IT a couple times last week, and since has been out of the office for quite a bit, it 
seems as if many projects have been put on hold. My understanding, though, is that MIT have been working on 
creating a copy of the Confidential items on a hard drive for us to give to the FBI, as well as a separate hard drive for our 
office to have that will contain everything we produced in the Sixth Production. 
Unfortunately, for the last two weeks or so, I've been having trouble connecting with anyone and getting a clear answer 
on its progress. I talked with Ken two weeks ago, and he said he'd confirm with and get back to me. I followed up, 
but still have heard nothing. Then, I talked with from IT on Friday morning, and he said that he would give a call 
Friday afternoon to check on the drive we had requested. He thought that it was still copying, but he was going to double 
check on its status. I followed up with IN Friday afternoon and again yesterday afternoon, but haven't heard anything 
back. I'll follow up again today and hopefully will get a responsel I'll keep you posted. 
Thank you for your patiencel Hopefully we'll get this resolved soon.
